name: Endor Celebration (V)
Lore: 'The Rebel presence on Endor meant that the Ewoks would be able to live free from the Empire''s tyranny.',
Text: 'Cancel an Effect with ''occupation'' in title. (Immune to Sense.) OR During your draw phase, if you have a Rebel scout alone at Back Door, draw destiny. Activate or retrieve 5 Force and place this Interrupt on bottom of Lost Pile if destiny < the number of your scouts on table.',
